This article is about the [[demographics|demographic]] features of the [[List of population of Canada by years|population]] of [[Canada]], including [[population density]], [[Ethnic group|ethnicity]], education level, health of the populace, economic status, religious affiliations and other aspects of the population, the [[People of Canada]].

