===Vowel nuclei===
There is little agreement as to the vowels of Khmer. This may be in part because political centralization has not been achieved, so standard Khmer does not prevail throughout Cambodia. As such, many speakers of even the same community may have different phonological inventories.&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web| url=http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/21736/1/jaas031010.pdf| title= On Takeo Dialects of Khmer: Phonology and World List| first=Makoto| last=Minegishi| year=1986| accessdate=2008-12-04}}&lt;/ref&gt; Two proposals follow:

{| class=&quot;wikitable&quot;
|+Khmer vowels I&lt;ref name=&quot;SIDWELL&quot; /&gt;
