|-
!Short vowels
| {{IPA|i}} || {{IPA|e}} || || {{IPA|ɨ}} || {{IPA|ə}} || {{IPA|ɐ}} || {{IPA|a}} || {{IPA|u}} || {{IPA|o}} ||
|-
!Long diphthongs
|{{IPA|iə̯}} || {{IPA|ei̯}} || {{IPA|ɐe̯}} || {{IPA|ɨə̯}} || {{IPA|əɨ̯}} || {{IPA|ɐə̯}} || {{IPA|ao̯}} || {{IPA|uə̯}} || {{IPA|ou̯}} || {{IPA|ɔə̯}}
