==Footnotes==
*{{note label|NamingNote|a|a}}According to the [[International Code of Zoological Nomenclature]] (ICZN) naming rules, the historically correct name for this family should be Microcebina, but the name Cheirogaleidae has been retained for stability.&lt;ref name=&quot;1997McKenna&quot; /&gt;
*{{note label|not_recognized|b|b}}In 2008, 7 new species of ''Microcebus'' were formally recognized, but ''Microcebus lokobensis'' ([[Lokobe Mouse Lemur]]) was not among the additions.  Therefore its status as a species is still questionable.&lt;ref name=Mittermeier2008/&gt;

